    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule where every curve tells a story of elegance and every mile is a brushstroke on the canvas of the open road. This isn't just a vehicle; it's a masterpiece of engineering, finished in a deep, lustrous hue that captures the golden hour even on the cloudiest days. Inside, the cabin greets you with the intoxicating aroma of preserved leather and the tactile satisfaction of polished chrome toggles. To drive this machine is to command a symphony of mechanical precision\u2014a purr that resonates through the chassis and into your soul. It stands as a testament to an era of uncompromising style, waiting for a curator who understands that some things don't just age; they become legends.",
      "price": 48500.0,
